## 1. Project Overview

**FlexStock** is a self-hostable, white-label inventory management system built as a single configurable codebase. It is sold or delivered to individual business clients who need to track their own products. Each client receives the full source code and deploys it on their own server.

The system is **product-agnostic by design**  meaning the same codebase handles a pharmacy, a clothing store, a hardware shop, or a warehouse without any code changes. All customization happens through an admin panel where the owner defines their product categories and custom fields.

### Who Is This For?

| Role | Description |
|---|---|
| **Developer (You)** | Builds and maintains the codebase, delivers to clients |
| **Business Owner** | Receives the system, configures it for their products, manages inventory |
| **Staff/Employees** | Uses the system daily to record stock movements, view levels |

