## 2. Goals & Non-Goals

### Goals

- One codebase, fully configurable per client via admin panel
- Real-time stock updates across all open browser sessions
- Dynamic product fields (no schema changes per client)
- Role-based access control (admin, manager, staff)
- Low-stock alerts and movement history
- Clean, professional export (PDF/Excel reports)
- Optional: barcode/price tag label printing
- Optional: sales tracking per transaction
- Professional GitHub repository with full documentation
- Easy one-command installation for non-technical clients

### Non-Goals

- This is NOT a SaaS / multi-tenant hosted platform
- No cloud billing, subscription management, or payment gateway (in core)
- No mobile app (web is responsive enough)
- No AI/ML demand forecasting (future roadmap)
- No e-commerce storefront

